data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Ensure Open condition P3 Jumper on the MMB test fixture by chnaging the P3 Jumper toggle switch position to "Open".
2. Ensure to Connect UART Adaptor connector to RS 232 SYST port of the fixture & connect the Ethernet cable on Fixture.
3. Configure the MMB board by typing below command in TERA TERAM setenv ipaddr 169.254.52.200 setenv netmask 255.255.0.0 ping 169.254.52.201 4. Verify the captured TERA TERAM Screenshot with left side reference image.
